{"tid":278892,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解仲手賤睇佢嘅野⋯⋯","createTime":"2017-06-10T19:42:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-11T06:06:22.000Z","uid":68777,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"92675c8492096e764907f9c4e0995f9552315025","tid":278892,"uid":68777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T19:42:54.000Z","msg":"點解你咁唔爭氣，人地日日開開心心同朋友打機出街食飯，你就仲喺度掛住以前。你嘅世界以後都係得番你自己，我唔明點解你仲要留戀佢。佢曾經愛過你咁又點，講分手果刻佢已經唔care會唔會失去你，你只係一件比人遺棄嘅垃圾，就算你點做佢都唔在乎你。過埋今日可唔可以唔好再成日掛住佢，好好咁為自己活。我知你好怕再去投入一段關係，但同時又覺得好空虛，但都要繼續行落去，知唔知呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a726b1c4b9f97b3496b37ac9d7eac4534018e49d","tid":278892,"uid":45756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T19:56:41.000Z","msg":"同你一樣 不過人地已經有新男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時唔小心見到佢同條仔啲相個心好痛<br />\n<br />\n但係自己又唔捨得unfollow佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我可以點做"},{"pid":"612578b999dd64d755e390c1a4e1e63c23c2228b","tid":278892,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T20:05:17.000Z","msg":"不要再說了"},{"pid":"fabf44d9cae9c3cdf1e7995cd07aff8ac57d7dff","tid":278892,"uid":89402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T20:18:42.000Z","msg":"原來只因深愛著..."},{"pid":"104e835c87228b9fffde02e59ab4b908ec8d82b7","tid":278892,"uid":70958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T20:19:49.000Z","msg":"ok<br />\n已經冇再留意"},{"pid":"de95c6681ac74a0e5745032ccd1c2a7ea2c5bb8b","tid":278892,"uid":13374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T20:20:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ok<br />\n已經冇再留意</blockquote><br />\nX2"},{"pid":"fdd41d83294bceff66ce367c6f2e46ed92eeab1a","tid":278892,"uid":82854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T20:25:39.000Z","msg":"盡量..."},{"pid":"85be72d279fc9b2699cae03d59bb90194e9dec0b","tid":278892,"uid":68777,"like":